Lmakla n yirden tezzuzur udem.
Yuḍen uzger, qqden aɣyul.
Dayen yeffeɣ waɛbar.
Yefruri zznad.
Tamekḥelt mm sin n yixenfyac.
Argaz, d win yettaṭṭafen deg wawal-
Argaz yettwaṭṭaf seg yiles.
Di ṭṭiq i d-ittban wergaz.
D lḥif i t-id-irebban.
Tekker-d di lḥif.
Yella waya.
Yella waya, yella wayen yugaren aya.
Ugarent-k txidas-ik!
yurew-d yimi-w aman.
